xt":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":36990,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2021\/09\/25\/khawatim-determine-akhirah\/","url_meta":{"origin":35035,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Khawatim: Final deeds determine fate in Hereafter","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"September 25, 2021","format":false,"excerpt":"Sahl ibn Sa\u2019d reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cVerily, the deeds are only judged by their endings.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 6607 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Bukhari Imam Ibn al-Mulaqqin commented, \"Allah judges His servants in good and evil, such that He forgives\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":10294,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/12\/14\/ummah-split-sects-jamaah\/","url_meta":{"origin":35035,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Ummah: Only the Jama&#8217;ah will go to Paradise","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"December 14, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"'Afw ibn Malik reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cThe Jews split into seventy-one sects, one of them is in Paradise and seventy are in the Hellfire. The Christians split into seventy-two sects, seventy-one are in the Hellfire and one of them is in\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":31991,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/06\/12\/his-adl-outweighs-jawr\/","url_meta":{"origin":35035,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Justice: He is in Paradise if his justice overcomes his injustice","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"June 12, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cWhoever seeks to be a judge over the Muslims such that he acquires it and his justice outweighs his tyranny, he will have Paradise. If his tyranny outweighs his justice, he will have Hellfire.\u201d Source: Sunan\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":19342,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2014\/06\/17\/hereafter-jannah-nar-dua\/","url_meta":{"origin":35035,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Akhirah: Paradise and Hellfire pray for believers","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"June 17, 2014","format":false,"excerpt":"Anas ibn Malik reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cWhoever asks Allah for Paradise three times, Paradise will say: O Allah, admit him into Paradise! Whoever seeks protection from Hellfire three times, Hellfire will say: O Allah, save him from the Hellfire!\u201d Source: Sunan\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":11700,"url":